  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Residence Alhena apartments are offered on a self catering board basis. </p>
<p>Meal delivery services including breakfast delivery is available to book locally, prices may vary.</p>
<p>There is an onsite restaurant and bar open for lunch and dinner. You are also a short distance away from the resort centre where there is a variety of restaurants serving French classics and international favourites.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
