  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Alhéna is a modern residence and hotel complex located close to the Flaine Forum and offering high-quality accommodations on the snow front. The Residence Alhena has been awarded the Green Key certification, <span><span class="ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">demonstrating their commitment to environmental preservation and highlighting its dedication to sustainable development within the tourism industry.</span></span></p>
<h2>Fantastic location</h2>
<p>The Alhéna is a luxurious residence in Flaine Forum, distinguished by its distinctive architecture and desirable location. The central location of this property, just steps from the town square and the base of the ski slopes, is undeniably an attractive feature. A slope-side location provides convenient access to the 265km of slopes in the Grand Massif Ski Area, where there are slopes for skiers of all skill levels, whether you are a  beginners or have been skiing for a while.</p>
<h2>Warm and welcoming apartments</h2>
<p>The newly built residence offers high quality apartments in the centre of Flaine Forum, and have all the facilities needed for a comfortable, with a fully equipped kitchen, cosy lounge and spacious bedrooms and access to the wellness area - these apartments tick all the boxes for a winter escape.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>Unwind and relax in the wellness area of the residence, which features a heated indoor pool, sauna, steam room, sensory showers, and Nordic bath. There is also a children's splash pool for the younger guests. Massages and treatments, as well as a relaxation area and Himalayan salt wall, can be reserved locally for a little extra treat. Alternatively, train for your next ski excursion in the fitness room, which features a variety of equipment.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
