  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> sleep up to six people and are around 65m². The apartments have a double bedroom with a shower room, a twin bedroom, living room with a double sofa bed, a balcony with a Forum view, kitchen and a bathroom with a bath. </p>
<p><strong>Grand comfort two bedroom</strong> apartments sleep two to six people and are around 65m². The Grand Comfort apartments have a double bedroom with a separate en-suite, a twin bedroom, a large kitchen opening onto the living room, and a balcony with outdoor furniture and a view of the slopes.<span> </span></p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments </strong>sleep up to eight people and are around 88m². The apartments have a double bedroom with a separate en-suite,  two twin bedrooms, <span>kitchen opening onto the living living room, and a balcony with outdoor furniture.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p>End of stay is included apart from the kitchen, which must be left clean before departure.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Beds made on arrival (except sofa beds)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi access</li>
<li>Balcony with outdoor furniture</li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchen with induction stove top, wine cellar, oven with microwave and toaster</li>
<li>Nespresso machine and kettle</li>
<li>Cleaning kit with products and two tea towels</li>
<li>Toiletries in bathrooms and shower room</li>
<li>Bathrobe and slippers</li>
<li>Linen and towels</li>
<li>Private ski locker equipped with boot and glove dryers</li>
<li>One parking space per apartment</li>
<li>Use of the wellness area  (swimming pool, whirlpool baths, sauna and hammam, fitness room)</li>
<li>Luggage storage</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning (except kitchen area)</li>
<li><span>Iron and ironing board (on request)</span></li>
<li><span>Raclette machine, fondue machine, waffle iron (on request)</span></li>
<li><span>Baby kits with cot, highchair and bottle warmer (free on request)</span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
